Package org.eclipse.nebula.widgets.pagination

Interface IPageContentProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PageResultContentProvider

    public interface IPageContentProvider
    When IPageLoader load paginated list, the method IPageLoader.loadPage(PageableController) returns a pagination structure (like PageResult, Spring Data Page etc...). This interface is used to returns total elements and paginated list from the returned pagination structure.
